I combed through memories,

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:39.680
trying to figure out
exactly where I failed as a parent.

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:43.016
But there are no simple answers.

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:44.960
I can't give you any solutions.

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:46.720
All I can do

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:50.120
is share what I have learned.

